                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2035Jerem">Cycle of
                                                  Jeremiah</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
              
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1685Bookof">Book of
                                                  Jeremiah</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘኮነ፡ ኀበ፡ ኤርምያስ፡ ወልደ፡ ኬልቅዩ፡ ዘእምካህናት፡
                  ዘይነብር፡ ውስተ፡ አናቶት፡ በብሔረ፡ ብንያም። ወኮነ፡ ቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ኀቤየ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ ኢዮስያስ፡ ወልደ፡ 
                  አሞጽ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ይሁዳ፡ አመ፡ ፲ ወ ፫ አመተ፡ መንግሥቱ። ወኮነ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ ኢዮአቂም፡ ወልደ፡ ኢዮስያስ፡ ንጉሠ፡ 
                  ይሁዳ፡ እስከ፡ ተፈጸመ፡ ፲ ወ ፩ አመተ፡ ሴዴቅያስ፡ ወልደ፡ ኢዮስያስ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ይሁዳ፡ እስከ፡ አመ፡ ተጼወወት፡ 
                  ኢየሩሳሌም፡ ዘኃምስ፡ ወርኅ። ወኮነ፡ ቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሀቤየ፡ ወይቤለኒ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘእንበለ፡ እፍጥርከ፡ 
                  እምከርሠ፡ እምከ፡ አእመርኩከ። ወዘእንበለ፡ ትፃእ፡ እማኅፀን፡ ቀደስኩከ፡ ወነቢየ፡ ረሰይኩከ፡ ለአሕዛብ፡</incipit>
                
                        <note>This text is the corrected version and follows the order of the Hebrew redaction. 
                <p>It is divided into chapters (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ምዕራፋት፡</foreign>). </p>
                           <p>Chapters 1-12 of the Ethiopic text correspond to chapters 1-15 of the Hebrew text.  </p>
                           <p>The Ethiopic chapter 13 corresponds to the Hebrew chapter 16:1-17:25. </p>
                           <p>After chapter 13, the chapters are no longer numbered. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምዕራፍ፡</foreign> is then inserted at the places which correspond to the following passages of the Hebrew text:</p>
                           <p>18:1; </p>
                           <p>19:1; </p>
                           <p>20:1;  20:14; </p>
                           <p>21:1; </p>
                           <p>22:1;  22:29; </p>
                           <p>24:1; </p>
                           <p>25:1; </p>
                           <p>26:1; </p>
                           <p>27:1; </p>
                           <p>28:1;  28:12; </p>
                           <p>29:30; </p>
                           <p>32:1;    32:26; </p>
                           <p>33:1;  33:19;  33:23; </p>
                           <p>34:1;    34:8; </p>
                           <p>35:1;  35:12; </p>
                           <p>36:1;  36:27;</p>
                           <p>37:1; </p>
                           <p>40:1; </p>
                           <p>41:1;  41:16;</p>
                           <p>43:1;  43:8; </p>
                           <p>44:1; </p>
                           <p>46:1; </p>
                           <p>47:1; </p>
                           <p>48:1; </p>
                           <p>49:1;  49:7;  49:23;  49:34; </p>
                           <p>50:1; </p>
                           <p>51:1;  51:59; </p>
                           <p>52:1</p>
                        </note>
                        <note>This text has been translated from the 
                <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1219Bible#t6greekLXX"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT1219Bible#t6greekLXX</span></ref>. 
                This is shown by a passage in 25:10 where the translation 
                <foreign xml:lang="gez">መዓዘ፡ <supplied reason="explanation" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">መዐዛ፡</supplied> ዕፍረት፡</foreign>
                (translating the <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1219Bible#t6greekLXX"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT1219Bible#t6greekLXX</span></ref>'s <foreign xml:lang="grc">ὀσμπὴν μύρου</foreign>) 
                is found next to <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቃለ፡ ማኅረፅ፡</foreign>,
                which corresponds more closely to the sense of the Hebrew <foreign xml:lang="he"> קול רחים</foreign>. 
              <p>The text was revised and rewritten according to a Hebrew original, which is shown by many Ethiopic roots, which have been employed here analogous to their Hebrew equivalents, 
                as well as some untranslated Hebrew words (<foreign xml:lang="he">נגב</foreign>,
                <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኖጌብ፡</foreign> 13:19;
               
          <foreign xml:lang="he">     כתרת</foreign>,
                <foreign xml:lang="gez"> ኰታሪት፡</foreign>  52:22).</p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
            
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="57r">Fols 57r and following</locus> 
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1202Bookof">Book of
                                                  Baruch</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዝነገረ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘጸሐፈ፡ ባሮክ፡ ወልደ፡ ኔርዩ፡ ወልደ፡ ማሴው፡ ወልደ፡ ሴዴቅዩ፡ ወልደ፡
              ኬልቅዩ፡ ባቢሎን፡ በኃምስ፡ ዓመት፡ በሰቡዓ፡ ሠርቅ፡ አመ፡ ነሥእዋ፡ ፋርስ፡ ለኢየሩሳሌም፡ ወአውዓይዋ።
              ወአንበበ፡ ባሮክ፡ ዘንተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ በኀበ፡ ኢኮንያስ፡ ወልደ፡ ኢዮአቄም፡ ንጉሠ፡ ይሁዳ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ሕዝብ፡
              ዘመጽአ፡ ወለእከ፡ ኀበ፡ ካህናት፡ ኢየሩሳሌም፡ አመ፡ ነሥኡ፡ ንዋየ፡ ቤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እምቤተ፡ መቅደስ፡ 
         </incipit>
                        <note>This text is given as an appendix to <ref target="#ms_i1">the Book of Jeremiah</ref>; according to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10747Zotenbe">Hermann Zotenberg</persName> 
                it is a mutilated translation of the Greek original</note>
                     </msItem>
            
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="59r">Fols 59r and following</locus>
                        <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1753Lament">ሰቆቃወ፡ ኤርምያስ፡ ነቢይ።</title>
                        <note>This version has been revised according to the Hebrew text; in 3:12 the Hebrew
                <foreign xml:lang="he">מטרא</foreign> has been preserved in the translation as 
                <foreign xml:lang="gez">መ ጠራ፡</foreign> 
                        </note>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ምዕራፍ፡ ፩። ወእምዝ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ፄወዎ፡ ለኤርምያስ፡ ወለኢየሩሳሌምኒ፡ 
                አማሰንዋ፡ ነበረ፡ 
              ኤርምያስ፡ ይበኪ፡ ወአስቆቀወ፡ ዘከመዝ፡ ሰቆቃወ፡ ላዕለ፡ ኢየሩሳሌም። አሌፍ፡ እፎ፡ ነበረት፡ ባሕቲታ፡ ሀገር፡
              እንተ፡ ምልዕት፡ ሕዝበ፡ ወትኴንን፡ በሐውርተ፡ ወገብአት፡ ውስተ፡ እደ፡ ፀዋር።</incipit>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
              
                     </msItem>
            
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="62v">Fols 62v and following</locus> 
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1686Epistl">Epistle of
                                                  Jeremiah</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">አርአያ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘኤርምያስ፡ ዘፈነወ፡ ኀበ፡ እለ፡ ጼወዎሙ፡ ሀገረ፡ ባቢሎን፡ ንጉሠ፡
                ባቢሎን፡
                ይንግርዎሙ፡ ዘአዘዘ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በእንተ፡ ኀጢአትክሙ፡ ዘአበስክሙ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ወሰዱክሙ፡ 
              ባቢሎን፡ ትንበሩ፡ ህየ፡ ብዙኀ፡ መዋዕለ፡ እስከ፡ ሳብዕ፡ ትውልድ።</incipit>
                        <note>This text, which is attached to <ref target="#ms_i1.3"/>, is mutilated
                similarly to <ref target="#ms_i1.2"/>. </note>
                     </msItem>
            
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <locus target="#63v">Fol. 63v</locus>
                        <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2193Prophe">ትንቢት፡ ዘኤርምያስ፡ ወይቤሎ፡
                ኤርምያስ፡ ለፋክሶር፡ ከማሁ፡ አንትሙሰ፡ በኵሉ፡ መዋዕሊክሙ፡ ትትቃረንዋ፡ ለጽድቅ<gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>
                        </title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     </msItem>
            
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                        <locus from="63v">Fols 63v and following</locus>
                        <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2167Parali">ተረፈ፡ ነገር፡ ዘባሮክ፡ ዘኢኮነ፡ ኅቡዓ፡ 
                ዘአመ፡ ፄወዉ፡ ባቢሎን።</title>
                        <explicit type="subscriptio" xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ በዝየ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ባሮክ፡ ወትሩፋተ፡ ነገሩ፡ ለኤርምያስ።</explicit>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
            
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="71r">Fols 71r and following</locus>
                     <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2358Sirach">ጥበብ፡ ዘሆሴዕ፡ ወልደ፡ ሲራክ።</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ቀዳሚሃ፡ ኵላ፡ ጥበብ፡ እምኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ይእቲ፡ ወምስሌሁ፡ ሀለወት፡ ለዓለም<supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">።</supplied>
              ኆፃ፡ ባሕር፡ ወነጠብጣበ፡ ዝናም፡ ወመዋዕለ፡ ዓለም፡ መኑ፡ ኈለቈ፡ ሉዓሌ፡ ሰማይ፡ ወራኅበ፡ ምድር፡ ወዕመቀ፡
              ቀላይ። ወለጥበብ፡ መኑ፡ ሰፈሮሙ <supplied reason="lost" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">።</supplied> 
                ቅድመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ተፈጥረት፡ ጥበብ፡ ወሕሊናሃ፡ ለጥበብ፡ ዘእምፍጥረተ፡ ዓለም <supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">።</supplied>
                ሥርዋ፡ ለጥበብ፡ ለመኑ፡ ተከሥተ፡ ወመኑ፡ አእመረ፡ ምክራ<supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">።</supplied>
                ፩ ጥበብ፡ ወፈድፋደ፡ ግሩም፡ ውእቱ፡ ወይነብር፡
              ላዕለ፡ መንበሩ፡ ውእቱ።</incipit>
                     <explicit type="subscriptio" xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ሲራክ፡ ዘተጽሕፈ፡ 
                በ<date>፷፻ ወ፻ ወ፸ ዓመት</date>።</explicit> 
                     <note>See for a discussion of the subscription:
                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/V5KW5Z9P"><seg type="encyclopediaArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Bausi2010EAEWisdom"/><title level="a">Wisdom books, biblical</title><title type="short">EAe</title><title level="m">Encyclopaedia Aethiopica</title><author><forename>Alessandro</forename><surname>Bausi</surname></author><editor><forename>Siegbert</forename><surname>Uhlig</surname></editor><editor><forename>Alessandro</forename><surname>Bausi</surname></editor><pubPlace>Wiesbaden</pubPlace><publisher>Harrassowitz Verlag</publisher><date>2010</date><biblScope unit="volume">IV</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">1189a-1191a</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Bausi2010EAEWisdom</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Bausi2010EAEWisdom</note><citedRange unit="page">1189b</citedRange></bibl>
