                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc type="Unclear">Amharic enumeration of villages and properties of some Ethiopian regions
                  at the end of the volume. The following is the beginning:</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="am">
                              <lb/> ኁልቈ፡ ምድር፡ ዘስረቀርን፡
                    <lb/>በፀዳ፡ ፫፻፵።
                    <lb/> በ ቢቸመር፡ ፵፬።
                    <lb/> በብላሄራ፡ ፫፻፷፯።</q>    
                        </item>
                     </list>
